metadata.name: The Crab
metadata.description:
A crab, a fish and a turtle jump rope under the sea. The crab wants to remind us a word; he jumps out of the water and the word in his mind is formed by splashing water out of the sea. NFT may change the lives of many people.

I made "The Crab" stop-motion animation under camera by photographing frame by frame.
